::KitKat::

She looked at her leg and the to Drillbit. "YEs, Get the others on 
the ship.  And when the other group of Predacons gets here, get them 
on Phobia's ship."  She looks at the new bot.  "Glad to have you with 
us.  Now Get on that ship and kill any maximal you can along the way."

She reopened her link,"HURRY UP AND GET ON PHOBIA'S SHIP.  WE NEED TO 
REGROUP AND THEN WE WILL SLAG THESE GUYS!"
